{"tid":468661,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[DPDR]人格解體/失實症","createTime":"2017-11-14T14:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T08:40:35.000Z","uid":24948,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"05b31863a2facd29e6aedd06cd325eee59a156c0","tid":468661,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:41:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>Depersonalization-Derealization Disorder </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>人格解體</strong><br />\n<br />\n患者訴述他的情感或內心體驗變得疏遠，陌生，不是他自己的，或已經喪失了，有的患者覺得他的情感和動作好像是別人的，或覺得他像在演戲;有的患者體驗到他的感覺已脫離了他的精神活動或軀體，好像是一位旁觀者;有的患者體驗到自己像一個機器人，像處於夢境之中;還有的患者訴述體驗不到自己的情感，或感覺喪失了對自己精神或軀體的支配，患者知道這類體驗是異常的，但持續或出現，無法消除，感到十分痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>現實解體</strong><br />\n<br />\n患者訴述周圍環境或特定物體看起來很陌生，變了形，很平淡，毫無生氣，枯燥無味，或者覺得周圍像一個舞台每個人都在這個舞台上演戲;可伴有時間或空間知覺的改變，患者的上述體驗如果呈發作性，可伴有頭昏，焦慮和恐懼，擔心自己會失去理智，或害怕這種現象再次出現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jiankanghou.com/jibing/39664.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiankanghou.com%2Fjibing%2F39664.html&d=hL4agABhR7TcQzK%2B8Mq0EL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2a1b0c11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.jiankanghou.com/jibing/39664.html</a><br />\n<br />\n連登好似無咩人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係reddit睇翻黎 有無巴絲打都有咁嘅感覺？好似唔係自己控制緊自己身體咁"},{"pid":"1992017a0559e15878f64a22b0f0b44989454d90","tid":468661,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"47a60bfdd5bb24bb0e849e9a53ad21ea9549b940","tid":468661,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:40:40.000Z","msg":"冇試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff49f375f31ec03a9f622443791d7741ae86684","tid":468661,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"點討論？"},{"pid":"07a78e99dd668ed255ae3832f6a9b29ca3eeaf33","tid":468661,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T22:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點討論？</blockquote><br />\n睇黎無咩巴打有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a6424a06e4efa13b6842b426839989a8e51bdb","tid":468661,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T22:58:55.000Z","msg":"一年前出現過類似人格解體症狀<br />\n但最終醫生診斷為抑鬱症<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c99cd6a67efc66b221996f1f392ef1974893dd","tid":468661,"uid":71205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T23:00:28.000Z","msg":"Push 關唔關人格分裂事？"},{"pid":"d0af964427d8f4fa6aaf20eb13fed4081c159574","tid":468661,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T21:25:33.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55347e734991c5d8929085258fe73648434a2b49","tid":468661,"uid":57228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"同抽離好似冇分別"},{"pid":"2eb6140aa48fa08d7d33cbc1934d08fd71243efa","tid":468661,"uid":5920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:53:46.000Z","msg":"我好細個開始咁 有冇人一樣"},{"pid":"1e44de88c9f9685ce7dfecd9c55e2f6fdef1993b","tid":468661,"uid":50869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"最近幾日出現呢種感覺 好無助 好想做番正常人 唔知有冇得醫"},{"pid":"fdd4ec77918348a36a26fb76060ff3f39bf1515b","tid":468661,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e44de88c9f9685ce7dfecd9c55e2f6fdef1993b","tid":468661,"uid":50869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"最近幾日出現呢種感覺 好無助 好想做番正常人 唔知有冇得醫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:11:11.000Z","msg":"我都係係reddit個度睇翻黎 巴打咁得閒對上黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己係幾年前有呢種感覺 覺得個人好似抽離左自己個身體咁 係第三方睇住自己咁 依家都仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" 